%% L1 to L2 Message Flow
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as USER/CONTRACT
    participant L1 as L1 (LineaRollup)
    participant Coord as Coordinator
    participant L2 as L2 (L2MessageService)

    User->>L1: 1. sendMessage()
    L1->>L1: 2. MessageSent event
    L1->>Coord: Event detected
    Coord->>L2: 3. Anchor hash
    L2->>L2: 4. Hash stored
    Note over L2: Message now CLAIMABLE
    User->>L2: 5. claimMessage()<br/>(or Postman)
    L2->>L2: 6. Execute calldata
    L2-->>User: Message delivered
